ZH: 在丈夫和妻子之间发生矛盾时，他们的父母应该隔岸观火。
EN: When conflicts arise between husband and wife, their parents should stay out of it.

ZH: 如果两个同事之间有矛盾，我们应该隔岸观火，避免掺和其中。
EN: If there is a conflict between two colleagues, we should stay out of it and not get involved.

ZH: 在朋友之间发生争执时，最好的做法是隔岸观火，让他们自行解决。
EN: When arguments arise between friends, the best approach is to stay out of it and let them resolve it themselves.

ZH: 在两个国家之间爆发战争的时候，其他国家应该隔岸观火，不要直接卷入。
EN: When war breaks out between two countries, other countries should stay out of it and not get directly involved.

ZH: 作为家长，当孩子们之间发生争执时，我们应该隔岸观火，让他们独立解决。
EN: As parents, when conflicts arise among our children, we should stay out of it and let them resolve it on their own.

ZH: 当同事之间发生矛盾时，老板应该隔岸观火，不要一味助纣为虐。
EN: When conflicts arise between colleagues, the boss should stay out of it and not blindly take sides.

ZH: 作为邻居，当两家之间发生争执时，我们应该隔岸观火，不要卷入其中。
EN: As neighbors, when disputes arise between two families, we should stay out of it and not get involved.

ZH: 在朋友之间的事务中，我们应该隔岸观火，不要帮忙助纣为虐。
EN: In matters between friends, we should stay out of it and not help to fuel the fire.

ZH: 当两个组织之间爆发争端时，其他组织应该隔岸观火，保持中立态度。
EN: When disputes arise between two organizations, other organizations should stay out of it and maintain a neutral stance.

ZH: 作为亲戚，当家庭成员之间发生矛盾时，我们应该隔岸观火，不要加剧情况。
EN: As relatives, when conflicts arise among family members, we should stay out of it and not worsen the situation.

ZH: 在商业竞争中，公司应该隔岸观火，不要使用不道德的手段。
EN: In business competition, companies should stay out of it and not use unethical means.

ZH: 当朋友之间产生矛盾时，我们应该隔岸观火，而不是一味地介入。
EN: When conflicts arise between friends, we should stay out of it and not blindly intervene.

ZH: 在国际冲突中，中立国家应该隔岸观火，不要加剧紛擾。
EN: In international conflicts, neutral countries should stay out of it and not escalate the turmoil.

ZH: 作为同事，当团队内部产生分歧时，我们应该隔岸观火，不要挑拨是非。
EN: As colleagues, when there are disagreements within the team, we should stay out of it and not sow discord.

ZH: 在家庭纷争中，邻居应该隔岸观火，不要添乱。
EN: In family disputes, neighbors should stay out of it and not make things worse.

ZH: 当两国关系紧张时，其他国家应该隔岸观火，避免被卷入。
EN: When relations between two countries are tense, other countries should stay out of it and avoid being dragged into it.

ZH: 在父母和孩子之间发生矛盾时，其他亲戚应该隔岸观火，不要加剧矛盾。
EN: When conflicts arise between parents and children, other relatives should stay out of it and not intensify the conflict.

ZH: 作为团队领导，当团队成员之间发生分歧时，我们应该隔岸观火，而不是一味地干涉。
EN: As team leaders, when disagreements arise among team members, we should stay out of it and not blindly interfere.

ZH: 在社会纷争中，政府部门应该隔岸观火，不要加剧空檔。
EN: In social conflicts, government departments should stay out of it and not escalate the situation.
